Files with `@ai-index` in first 50 lines have a section map.

**Reading indexed files:**
1. Check lines 1-50 for `@ai-index` table
2. Find section: `| store/nodes | 180 | 350 |`
3. Read only that range: lines 180-350

**After editing:** Update End for edited section, shift all sections below.

**Example table:**
```
| Section     | Line | End  |
|-------------|------|------|
| imports     |    1 |   45 |
| store/nodes |  180 |  350 |
| store/edges |  352 |  480 |
```
